12. Conclusion
---------------
ScheduleSync now implements core group scheduling features: real-time mutual availability, direct group event suggestion/response, and friend-based privacy controls. Our design/codebase prioritize ease of use for students. Testing confirms our technical approach is robust. Future plans include notifications, advanced friend/group management, and UI optimization.
